CANNOT_FIND_PERMISSION_GROUP: The permission group does not exist.
PERMISSION_GROUP_IS_USING: There is a user or access key using that permission group.
ALREADY_EXISTS_PLATFORM_NAME: There is already a platform of the same name.
INVALID_EMAIL_OR_PASSWORD: Your email or password is incorrect.
INVALID_PHONE_OR_PASSWORD: Your phone number or password is incorrect.
NOT_CONNECTED_WITH_METHOD: It is not linked with the authentication method.
ALREADY_USING_EMAIL: This email is already in use by another user.
ALREADY_USING_PHONE: The phone number is already in use by another user.
